<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">University of Massachusetts Amherst</h2>
<strong>Amherst, MA</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>UMass Amherst grants advanced standing and/or credit for the College Board AP exams, but these credits vary depending upon scores and subject matter.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.umass.edu/admissions/apply/transferring-credit" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

 <p class="box-padding-3">
    Additional restrictions and requirements may apply to the policy listed below. For more detailed information, visit the college's AP policy on the Web or contact the college directly.
 </p>

